    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、おかしいな\n昨日はあんなにカッコ良く決まってたのに",
      "startTime": 5.1456386484,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3487.6946451999993,
          "startTime": 8.6333332936
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます\n……なんですか、そのぼさぼさ頭は",
      "startTime": 12.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "その……自分でヘアセットしようとしたんですが\n美容院でしてもらった時みたいにうまくいかなくて……",
      "startTime": 19.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁでも、これはこれで\n無造作ヘアって感じでいいかな～とか……はは……",
      "startTime": 25.146295093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "無造作ヘアは緻密な計算の上に成り立っているんです\n貴方のはただの無造作です",
      "startTime": 35.3000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく。せっかく綺麗に整えてもらったのに\nどうしたら一晩でそんな頭になるんですか",
      "startTime": 41.9000012715,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clipper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.665395199998,
          "startTime": 47.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしようもないですね\nやっぱりこのバリカンで刈るしか……",
      "startTime": 47.0333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "は、ははは……mihoさんはいつもキマってますよね\n良かったらセットについて教えてくれませんか？",
      "startTime": 55.3000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "特に教える義理はないですが……\n私は毎日ヘアアイロンを通してセットしています",
      "startTime": 62.0666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "髪が傷まないようにセット前にオイルを塗ったり\n髪に優しいスタイリング剤を使ったりはしていますね",
      "startTime": 68.6000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "あとは、寝る前の準備も大事です\n乾かさずに寝たりするなんてもってのほかです",
      "startTime": 75.5333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、貴方にこんなこと話しても\n馬の耳に念仏でしょうけど",
      "startTime": 81.5666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "う……耳が痛いです……でも確かに、mihoさんの髪\n凄く綺麗ですよね。日々の努力の賜物なんですね",
      "startTime": 90.1333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前です。アイドルとして\n髪の手入れは怠りません",
      "startTime": 97.3666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ今度CMを撮影するブランドの\nヘアケア用品は愛用していましたし",
      "startTime": 102.0896657639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "夏と冬で違うタイプのシャンプーを\n使い分けていたりします",
      "startTime": 106.8000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、それがCMに繋がるなんてことは\n考えてもみませんでしたが",
      "startTime": 111.8000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "良かったですね、CMが決まって\n俺も楽しみです",
      "startTime": 116.9855152498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか。あ、そういえばブランドから\nメンズ用のサンプルも届いていましたよね",
      "startTime": 123.2000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "使ってみたらどうですか？　セット用品もあるみたい\nですし、今すぐそのざんばらヘアを直して下さい",
      "startTime": 129.0886191521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、シャンプーのほかにワックスもあるみたいですね\nえっと……ジェルにスティックタイプに……？",
      "startTime": 137.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん、これ……\nどうやって使えばいいんですか……？",
      "startTime": 144.5387574192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私に聞くんですか\n裏の説明を読めばいいじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 149.4333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "私はこれから用事があるので\n貴方に構っている暇はありませんから",
      "startTime": 154.1333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、どこに行くんですか？",
      "startTime": 156.7000019947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "美容院です。撮影に向けて\n特別なケアをしてもらわないといけませんから",
      "startTime": 161.7666679382,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5735.962304899999,
          "startTime": 167.5026302431
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "それでは失礼します\n……ふんふーん……",
      "startTime": 168.2666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "今、mihoさん鼻歌歌ってた？\nいや、まさかな……",
      "startTime": 174.2333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 177.333335328,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.6646323,
          "startTime": 181.6999999603
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふんふーん……あ、mihoさん！\n早速もらったワックスを使ってみたんですけど",
      "startTime": 183.6666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "……なんですかそのツンツンした頭は\nfranが楽屋で観ていたアニメキャラみたいです",
      "startTime": 190.2000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "それに、どうしてそんなに嬉しそうなんですか\n髪だけじゃなくて、頭までどうかしてしまいましたか",
      "startTime": 197.0666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "だ、ダメですかね……\n朝、動画を見ながら頑張ってセットしたんですが……",
      "startTime": 202.9000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_02-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、どんな動画を見たんですか。セットの一つも\n出来ないなんて本当に情けないマネージャーですね",
      "startTime": 211.7333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
